These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
Transport: motorbike, helicopter, roller, tram
1. Transport:motorbike is on the left of Transport:tram##1
2. Transport:helicopter is on the right of Transport:roller##1
3. Transport:motorbike is on the right of Transport:helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Transport   | roller | helicopter | motorbike | tram |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
